        "body": "Thanks [~piaoyu zhang] for the clarification! It seems a configuration problem to me, that is, the configuration change is not propagated to all NMs. I tested it in CDH YARN cluster, could not reproduce the problem. Can you please specify what version of hadoop you were running? ",
